Other related events include {{ill|rice planting dances|ja|田植踊|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/rice planting dances|qq=}} and regional performances like {{ill|Hachinohe Enburi|ja|八戸のえんぶり|1=Enburi|2=ja|3=えんぶり|lt=Hachinohe Enburi|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hachinohe Enburi|13=User:Immanuelle/Enburi|qq=}} in {{ill|Tohoku|ja|東北地方|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tohoku|qq=}}.
== Notable Examples of Ta-asobi ==
* The {{ill|Itabashi Ta-asobi|ja|板橋の田遊び|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itabashi Ta-asobi|qq=}}, a {{ill|Nationally Designated Important Intangible Folk Cultural Property|ja|重要無形民俗文化財|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nationally Designated Important Intangible Folk Cultural Property|qq=}} of {{ill|Itabashi Ward|ja|板橋区|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itabashi Ward|qq=}}, {{ill|Tokyo|ja|東京都|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokyo|qq=}}. * The "Tsurumi Ta-asobi," a {{ill|Yokohama City Registered Regional Cultural Property|ja|横浜市登録地域文化財|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokohama City Registered Regional Cultural Property|qq=}} performed at {{ill|Tsurumi Shrine|ja|鶴見神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsurumi Shrine|qq=}} in {{ill|Tsurumi Ward|ja|鶴見区|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsurumi Ward|qq=}}, {{ill|Yokohama|ja|横浜市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokohama|qq=}}.<ref name=Tsurumi/><ref>[https://www.city.yokohama.lg.jp/kurashi/kyodo-manabi/bunkazai/bunya12000.files/0007_20191120.pdf Yokohama City Cultural Property List (PDF)]</ref> * The "Fujimori Ta-asobi," a Nationally Designated Important Intangible Folk Cultural Property in {{ill|Yaizu City|ja|焼津市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yaizu City|qq=}}, {{ill|Shizuoka Prefecture|ja|静岡県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shizuoka Prefecture|qq=}}. * The "Hirugaya Ta-asobi," performed at {{ill|Hiruko Shrine (Makinohara)|ja|蛭児神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hiruko Shrine (Makinohara)|qq=}} in {{ill|Makinohara City|ja|牧之原市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Makinohara City|qq=}}, {{ill|Shizuoka Prefecture|ja|静岡県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shizuoka Prefecture|qq=}}, also a Nationally Designated Important Intangible Folk Cultural Property. * The "Takizawa Ta-asobi," performed at Takizawa Yasaka Shrine in {{ill|Fujieda City|ja|藤枝市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujieda City|qq=}}, Shizuoka Prefecture, designated as an {{ill|Important Intangible Cultural Property|ja|無形民俗文化財|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Important Intangible Cultural Property|qq=}} of Shizuoka Prefecture. * The "Mishima Ta-asobi," performed at {{ill|Mishima Taisha|ja|三嶋大社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mishima Taisha|qq=}} in {{ill|Mishima City|ja|三島市|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mishima City|qq=}}, Shizuoka Prefecture, also an Important Intangible Cultural Property of Shizuoka Prefecture. * The "Oguni Shrine Ta-asobi," performed at {{ill|Okuni Shrine|lt=Okuni Shrine|lt=Oguni Shrine|ja|小國神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oguni Shrine|qq=}} in {{ill|Mori Town, Shuchi District|ja|森町|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mori Town, Shuchi District|qq=}}, {{ill|Shizuoka Prefecture|ja|静岡県|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shizuoka Prefecture|qq=}}, designated as a {{ill|Intangible Folk Cultural Properties Requiring Documentation|lt=Intangible Folk Cultural Properties Requiring Documentation|lt=Selected Intangible Folk Cultural Property|ja|選択無形民俗文化財|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Selected Intangible Folk Cultural Property|qq=}}.
