cture. * The "Oguni Shrine Ta-asobi," performed at {{ill|Okuni Shrine|lt=Okuni Shrine|lt=Oguni Shrine|ja|小國神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oguni Shrine|qq=}} in {{ill|Mori Town, Shuchi District|ja|森町|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mori Town, Shuchi District|qq=}}, [[:en:Shizuoka Prefecture|Shizuoka Prefecture]], designated as a {{ill|Intangible Folk Cultural Properties Requiring Documentation|lt=Intangible Folk Cultural Properties Requiring Documentation|lt=Selected Intangible Folk Cultural Property|ja|選択無形民俗文化財|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Selected Intangible Folk Cultural Property|qq=}}.
