* The {{ill|Itabashi Ta-asobi|ja|板橋の田遊び|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itabashi Ta-asobi|qq=}}, a {{ill|Nationally Designated Important Intangible Folk Cultural Property|ja|重要無形民俗文化財|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nationally Designated Important Intangible Folk Cultural Property|qq=}} of [[:en:Itabashi|Itabashi Ward]], [[:en:Tokyo|Tokyo]]. * The "Tsurumi Ta-asobi," a {{ill|Yokohama City Registered Regional Cultural Property|ja|横浜市登録地域文化財|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokohama City Registered Regional Cultural Property|qq=}} performed at {{ill|Tsurumi Shrine|ja|鶴見神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsurumi Shrine|qq=}} in {{ill|Tsurumi Ward|ja|鶴見区|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsurumi Ward|qq=}}, [[:en:Yokohama|Yokohama]].<ref name=Tsurumi/><ref>[https://www.city.yokohama.lg.jp/kurashi/kyodo-manabi/bunkazai/bunya12000.files/0007_20191120.pdf Yokohama City Cultural Property List (PDF)]</ref> * The "Fujimori Ta-asobi," a Nationally Designated Important Intangible Folk Cultural Property in [[:en:Yaizu|Yaizu City]], [[:en:Shizuoka Prefecture|Shizuoka Prefecture]]. * The "Hirugaya Ta-asobi," performed at {{ill|Hiruko Shrine (Makinohara)|ja|蛭児神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hiruko Shrine (Makinohara)|qq=}} in [[:en:Makinohara|Makinohara City]], [[:en:Shizuoka Prefecture|Shizuoka Prefecture]], also a Nationally Designated Important Intangible Folk Cultural Property. * The "Takizawa Ta-asobi," performed at Takizawa Yasaka Shrine in [[:en:Fujieda, Shizuoka|Fujieda City]], Shizuoka Prefecture, designated as an {{ill|Important Intangible Cultural Property|ja|無形民俗文化財|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Important Intangible Cultural Property|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 民俗文化財}} of Shizuoka Prefecture. * The "Mishima Ta-asobi," performed at [[:en:Mishima Taisha|Mishima Taisha]] in [[:en:Mishima, Shizuoka|Mishima City]], Shizuoka Prefecture, also an Important Intangible Cultural Property of Shizuoka Prefecture. * The "Oguni Shrine Ta-asobi," performed at {{ill|Okuni Shrine|lt=Okuni Shrine|lt=Oguni Shrine|ja|小國神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oguni Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 小国神社}} in {{ill|Mori Town, Shuchi District|ja|森町|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mori Town, Shuchi District|qq=}}, [[:en:Shizuoka Prefecture|Shizuoka Prefecture]], designated as a {{ill|Intangible Folk Cultural Properties Requiring Documentation|lt=Intangible Folk Cultural Properties Requiring Documentation|lt=Selected Intangible Folk Cultural Property|ja|選択無形民俗文化財|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Selected Intangible Folk Cultural Property|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 記録作成等の措置を講ずべき無形の民俗文化財}}.
